column5:
Sent an email days ago asking about the Alfana and would like to know what Bianchi bikes you have for sale.  I am traveling to Reno this coming weekend to visit family and would like to come by your shop.  I just purchased a trex and then a specialized but neither fits what I am really looking for.  Sold the trex and still ride the specialized for now.

Hope to hear from you soon..........Ginger
